    "generation_notes": "Path to Exile oracle: 'Exile target creature. Its controller may search their library for a basic land card, put that card onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.' Cost {W}. After resolution: Llanowar Elves goes to exile zone, p2 may search library for basic land. If p2 searches, Plains enters battlefield tapped and library is shuffled. The 'may' means p2 can decline; in this script p2 chooses to search and finds a Forest. Initial: p1 has Path to Exile with {W} in pool; p2 has Llanowar Elves on battlefield and 1 Forest in library.",
